document_data.name: House Symryvvin
document_data.mainbody: '''House Symryvvin''' was for centuries the 18th [[drow]] house of [[Menzoberranzan]].
document_data.Headquarters: House Symryvvin's compound in [[West Wall]] was five-sided, surrounded by both stalagtites and stalagmites. It was located just northeast of the tip of the [[Westrift]].
document_data.Members:
* [[Hesken-P'aj Symryvvin]]: [[Matron mother]]
* [[Halavin Symryvvin]]: A student at [[Arach-Tinilith]], fond of wearing jewelry. She attempted to kill [[Quenthel Baenre]] in [[1372 DR]].
